        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your sporting goods and fitness equipment handy with the Jumbo Aluminum Carabiner!\r\n\r\nThe Jumbo Carabiner is a great item to bring along camping, hiking, to the gym and just about any outdoor activity. Attach one to your backpack, water bottle, keys or purse to keep things handy and organized.\r\n\r\nThese carabiners are constructed of durable aluminum and feature a soft cushion grip for added comfort. They come in 6 colors: black, silver, red, green, blue and pink.\r\n\r\nThe jumbo carabiners also make a great handle for dog-walking! Attach it to your favorite leash and you'll have a sturdy, comfortable handle. Make sure to grab a few of these to keep around the house, your office or outdoor gear!\r\n\r\nPlease note: these carabiners are NOT FOR CLIMBING.",
